  "title": "Car Mechanic  汽车维修员",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide technical expertise in motor vehicle servicing, troubleshooting, and repairs to Company standards</li><li>Work closely as a team with the Supervisor and Service Advisors, explaining technical terms and providing feedback accordingly when handling every customer’s vehicle that is allocated to you.</li><li>Ensure that the workstation you are allocated to for every servicing/repair job is cleaned and neat before and after each servicing/repair job</li><li>Work on servicing jobs tasked to you by your supervisor individually, unless arranged otherwise</li><li>Execute any other tasks as required by the supervisor </li><li>Min 3 years relevant working experience</li><li>Monday to Friday 9-6 pm, Saturday 9-1 pm</li></ul><p><strong>Work location in Sin Ming area</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>To apply for this job, please contact 96788908</p>",
